item.description: I’m a first year Masters student at the University of Alberta. I am broadly interested in reinforcement learning as an approach to building autonomous agents. I am currently working on the problem of sample-efficient reinforcement with a focus on model-based RL. I am being supervised by Martha White and Erik Talvitie. You can download my CV here.
